author: James Ramage
title: Dollar Weakens Ahead of Fed Meeting
text:
The dollar slid broadly on Monday as investors booked profits on recent gains after disappointing housing numbers underscored how U.S. economic data remain uneven ahead of the Federal Reserve monetary-policy meeting.
